                    </div>

                    <div class="bgrid">

                        <h3>Can I be a host and a customer both?</h3>

                        <p>Absolutely. You can go out and have a meal and also you can host an event.</p>

                    </div>

                    <div class="bgrid">

                        <h3>How will the money be deducted?</h3>

                        <p>When you register, you will be asked for a credit card number. After every meal, we'll deduct the respective amount.</p>

                    </div>

                    <div class="bgrid">

                        <h3>How can I cancel my booking?</h3>

                        <p>There will be a few cancellation charges. If you are cancelling the event way too early than the event day, then it is very likely that we will not charge you.</p>

